INSERT INTO `mx_motor` VALUES (1,5,'sample motor1','sample-motor1','CG offers both Squirrel Cage (TPC & FTC Range) and Slip Ring (TPR & FTA Range) motors in horizontal (IMB3), vertical (IMV1) and inclined (IMB5, IMV5) mounting options to suit every customer requirement.','<p>Built in accordance with IEC 60034-1 / IS 325 standards, we offer customized, energy efficient and intelligent motors for various applications in IP23 & IP55 enclosures. We offer a wide range of cooling systems ranging from Self Circulation type (IC611) to independent forced circulation circuits (C616) and Tube Ventilated (IC511) to fin cooled (IC411) types.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nThe motors offered ranging from Open Air Circuit (IC01) and Closed Air Circuit (IC611) to independent externally fed air circuit (IC616). These are designed for optimum performance in adherence with application and site requirements of performance and space.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nThese motors have been designed to meet diversified application demands, while maintaining excellent performance and the highest quality. The robust design helps function with variable voltage, variable frequency drives</p>','special-application-motors_29034547-1.jpg',0),(2,2,'High Voltage Motors','high-voltage-motors','CG offers both Squirrel Cage (TPC & FTC Range) and Slip Ring (TPR & FTA Range) motors in horizontal (IMB3), vertical (IMV1) and inclined (IMB5, IMV5) mounting options to suit every customer requirement.','<p>Built in accordance with IEC 60034-1 / IS 325 standards, we offer customized, energy efficient and intelligent motors for various applications in IP23 & IP55 enclosures. We offer a wide range of cooling systems ranging from Self Circulation type (IC611) to independent forced circulation circuits (C616) and Tube Ventilated (IC511) to fin cooled (IC411) types.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nThe motors offered ranging from Open Air Circuit (IC01) and Closed Air Circuit (IC611) to independent externally fed air circuit (IC616). These are designed for optimum performance in adherence with application and site requirements of performance and space.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nThese motors have been designed to meet diversified application demands, while maintaining excellent performance and the highest quality. The robust design helps function with variable voltage, variable frequency drives.</p>','low-voltage-motors_09040708-2.jpg',0),(3,5,'Low Voltage Motors','low-voltage-motors',NULL,'<p>CG has an exemplary facility with an established manufacturing range of low voltage motors. All the manufacturing units are well supported by robust infrastructure. With world class infrastructure, we are satisfactorily meeting the clientΓÇÖs expectations. We have employed the most sophisticated and inclusive range of equipment and machinerys to carry out the bulk or customized order in most hassle-free and timely manner. Our core competencies lie in our manufacturing facility conforming to the international quality standards. In our continuous effort, to bring out the latest, most advanced product into market-place we continuously add many new services, features and introduce new innovative solutions so as to ensure complete customer satisfaction.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor better reliability of windings, we are using automated coil formation & Insertion machines. The┬á ┬áwindings are impregnated in VPI Plant. All the motors manufactured undergo rigorous testing at a computerized test plant.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLow Voltage (LV) AC motors range cast iron and aluminium motors conforming to IEC and NEMA MG 1 Standards.</p>','low-voltage-motors_09040708.jpg',0),(4,6,'Energy Efficient Motors','energy-efficient-motors',NULL,'<p>Efficient use of energy enables commercial and industrial facilities to minimize production costs, increase profits, and stay competitive. The majority of electrical energy consumed in most industrial facilities is used to run electric motors. Energy-efficient motors now available are typically from 2 to 6 percent more efficient than their standard counterparts. This efficiency Improvement translates into substantial energy and money savings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CG offers an entire range of energy efficient motors as per the latest IEC, IS & NEMA standards and also complies with the ┬áefficiency norms of each geographies.</p>','low-voltage-motors_09040708-1.jpg',0),(5,4,'Motors for Hazardous Areas (HV)','motors-for-hazardous-areas-hv',NULL,'<p>CG is fully geared to manufacture and supply a complete range of hazardous low voltage motors designed to suit the ignitable atmospheres present in hazardous Locations such as Zone1, Zone 2 or Class1 Div 1 and 2. The motors are tested in nationally and internationally affiliated Laboratories and are approved by BASEEFA for ATEX, CSA for IEC and Ex Div 2 and DGMS / CCO for complete range of low voltage hazardous motors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are the first manufacturers in India to develop motors complying with the requirements suitable for Group IIC (For Hydrogen Gas). With the advantage of meeting all the technical standards applicable for Oil and Gas industry, we cater efficiently to all the Oil companies┬á for their Off-Shore Platforms and Refineries projects.</p>','motors-for-hazardous-areas_18053121.jpg',0),(6,3,'Motors for Hazardous Area (LV)','motors-for-hazardous-area-lv',NULL,'<p>CG has the largest manufacturing range of low voltage motors suitable for hazardous area. These motors are designed to suit the ignitable atmospheres present in hazardous locations such as Zone1, Zone 2 or Class1 Div 1 and 2. Motors are suitable for various temperature classes & gas groups. CG manufactures ExΓÇÖeΓÇÖ , ExΓÇÖnAΓÇÖ & ExΓÇÖdΓÇÖ enclosure motors. The motors are licensed by BASEEFA for ATEX, CSA for IEC and Ex Div 2 and DGMS / CCO for complete range of low voltage hazardous motors.</p>','motors-for-hazardous-areas_18053121-1.jpg',0),(7,7,'DC Motors','dc-motors',NULL,'<p>CG is an established name synonymous with rotating machines. Today, we are in a position to offer an ENTIRE RANGE of world Class DC Motors. We offer laminated Yoke DC Motors in IEC frame up to 710, for various applications for constant and variable speed requirements.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nApplications:<br />\r\nPlastic extruders, Printing machines, Steel Rolling Mills, Wire Rod Mills, Apron Feeder, etc.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIndustries:<br />\r\nSugar, Textile, Rubber, Cement, etc</p>','motors-for-hazardous-areas_18053121-2.jpg',0),(8,8,'Special Application Motors','special-application-motors',NULL,'<p>We manufacture motors for special applications. Some of them include Double Cage Motor for Cement Mill, GD Series Brake Motor, Oil Well Pump Motor and Re-rolling Mill motor.</p>','special-application-motors_29034547.jpg',0),(9,8,'Energy Efficient Motors','energy-efficient-motors','sample motor1 subtitle','<p>Efficient use of energy enables commercial and industrial facilities to minimize production costs, increase profits, and stay competitive. The majority of electrical energy consumed in most industrial facilities is used to run electric motors. Energy-efficient motors now available are typically from 2 to 6 percent more efficient than their standard counterparts. This efficiency Improvement translates into substantial energy and money savings.<br />\r\n┬á</p>','img4-min-1-1.jpg',0),(10,9,'Motors for Hazardous Area (LV)','motors-for-hazardous-area-lv',NULL,'<p>CG has the largest manufacturing range of low voltage motors suitable for hazardous area. These motors are designed to suit the ignitable atmospheres present in hazardous locations such as Zone1, Zone 2 or Class1 Div 1 and 2. Motors are suitable for various temperature classes & gas groups. CG manufactures ExΓÇÖeΓÇÖ , ExΓÇÖnAΓÇÖ & ExΓÇÖdΓÇÖ enclosure motors. The motors are licensed by BASEEFA for ATEX, CSA for IEC and Ex Div 2 and DGMS / CCO for complete range of low voltage hazardous motors.</p>','mb-centrifugal-monoset-pump__530x530.webp',0),(11,7,'Laminated Yoke DC Motor','laminated-yoke-dc-motor',NULL,'<p>Laminated Yoke DC Motors are used mainly in Steel Industries, Lube oil Pump applications, Paper Mill, Printing Machines etc.┬á</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p>CG offers Laminated Yoke DC Motors from Framesize 100 to 500.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p>These DC Motors are available in various voltages such as 440 VDC, 220 VDC, 110 VDC and IP protection IP23 and IP55.┬á┬á</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>','dc_motor_24093013-2.jpg',0),(12,14,'Slip Ring Induction Motors','slip-ring-induction-motors',NULL,'<p>CG offers Low Voltage Slip Ring electric motors that range from **3.7 kW** to **350 kW** in both TEFC (IP55) and Drip Proof (IP23) construction. These motors are designed with a new Slip Ring and brush gear arrangement for trouble-free operations and long-lasting brush life. The Slip Ring is moulded in epoxy-based insulation and has excellent stability in operation at high temperature and very good anti-tracking property. CG also complies with IPSS standards to meet the requirements of Steel Plants.</p>','slip_ring_motors_lv_17044845.jpg',0),(13,17,'Motor third level testing','motor-third-level-testing','sample motor1 subtitle',NULL,'motors-for-hazardous-area-lv_29121345-1.jpg',0),(14,3,'bajaj motor','bajaj-motor',NULL,'<p>Bajaj FHP (Fractional Horsepower) motors are reliable single-phase and three-phase motors designed for household, commercial, and light industrial applications. These motors offer excellent performance with low power consumption.</p>\n\n<p>Available in various power ratings with robust construction, Bajaj motors are widely used in ceiling fans, water pumps, and small machine tools. All motors comply with Indian Standards and are manufactured with premium quality materials ensuring long operational life and reliability.</p>',NULL,0),(15,20,'Air Cooled Induction Motors','air-cooled-induction-motors-ic-6a1a1','IC 6A1A1, IC 6A1A6, IC 6A6A6 (CACA)','<p>CG Air Cooled Induction Motors (CACA) include TP and FT Series High Voltage motors with totally enclosed construction. The TPC range consists of foot mounted (IMB3) machines, which comply with both IS 2253 and IEC 60034-7.</p>\n\n<p>These motors feature totally enclosed IP55 protection as per IS 4691 / IEC 60034-5 and cooling with air to air heat exchangers comply with IEC 60034-6. Available in various power ratings and frame sizes suitable for industrial applications requiring reliable, efficient operation.</p>\n\n<p>All air cooled motors are designed for optimum performance in adherence with application and site requirements of performance and space. These motors have been designed to meet diversified application demands while maintaining excellent performance and the highest quality standards.</p>','HV-Air-Cooled-Induction-Motors.webp',1),(16,20,'Double Cage Motor for Cement Mill','double-cage-motor-cement-mill','Heavy Duty Cement Mill Application','<p>Double Cage Motor for Cement Mill applications from CG - a cost-effective alternative to the traditional slip ring motors for twin drives. These motors feature dual cage designs optimized for starting and running conditions.</p>\n\n<p>The double cage design provides excellent starting torque while maintaining full-load efficiency. These motors are particularly suitable for cement mill applications including raw mill, coal mill, and finish mill operations with various power ratings available.</p>\n\n<p>All double cage motors meet international standards and are tested for reliability in harsh industrial cement manufacturing environments. The specialized design ensures smooth acceleration and consistent performance under varying load conditions typical of cement mill operations.</p>','HV-Double-Cage-Cement-Mill.webp',1),(17,20,'Water Cooled Induction Motors','water-cooled-induction-motors-ic-8a1w7','IC 8A1W7 (CACW)','<p>Water Cooled Induction Motors (CACW) from CG include UW and FR Series High Voltage motors with advanced cooling technology. These motors feature water cooling systems designed for maximum thermal efficiency and reliable operation in continuous duty applications.</p>\n\n<p>The water cooling design allows for higher power density and superior thermal management compared to air-cooled alternatives. Available in various power ratings with IC 8A1W7 cooling configuration for industrial applications requiring efficient heat dissipation.</p>\n\n<p>All water cooled motors are engineered for optimum performance in demanding industrial environments. These motors are built to the highest quality standards conforming to international specifications and providing exceptional reliability and durability.</p>','HV-Water-Cooled-Motors.webp',1),(18,20,'Open Air Type Induction Motor','open-air-type-induction-motor','IC 0A1, IC 0A6 (SPDP)','<p>Open Air Type Induction Motor (SPDP) - Screen Protected Drip Proof motors from CG with IC 0A1 and IC 0A6 cooling configurations. These motors feature open construction with protective screens preventing direct liquid entry while allowing natural air circulation.</p>\n\n<p>The SPDP design provides cost-effective cooling solution for applications where completely sealed enclosures are not required. Available in various power ratings suitable for industrial machinery, fans, and equipment operating in relatively dry environments.</p>\n\n<p>All open air motors are designed for reliable performance with minimal maintenance requirements. These motors offer excellent cooling efficiency and are built to international standards ensuring superior performance and long operational life.</p>','HV-Open-Air-Motors.webp',1),(19,20,'Tube Ventilated Induction Motor','tube-ventilated-induction-motor','IC 5A1A1, IC 5A1A6 (TETV)','<p>Tube Ventilated Induction Motor (TETV) - CG manufactures totally enclosed tube ventilated motors (IC 5A1A1, IC 5A1A6) in both Squirrel Cage and Slip Ring designs that provide excellent performance in the most demanding environments and load conditions.</p>\n\n<p>The TV Series represents TETV motors most suitable for extreme dusty, humid and polluted atmospheres. TV Series Motors are used in industries such as Cement, Steel, Rubber, Paper, Refineries, Petrochemical and Fertilizer units as well as Power Generation plants.</p>\n\n<p>These motors feature tube ventilation systems that prevent dust and moisture ingress while maintaining effective cooling. All tube ventilated motors are built with robust construction and tested for reliability in harsh industrial environments.</p>','HV-Tube-Ventilated-Motors.webp',1),(20,20,'Fan Cooled Induction Motor','fan-cooled-induction-motor-tefc','IC 4A1A1, IC 4A1A6 (TEFC)','<p>Fan Cooled Induction Motor (TEFC) - CG NG-Series represents state-of-the-art, energy efficient and totally enclosed fan cooled (IC 4A1A1, IC 4A1A6) squirrel cage motors. These motors are extremely efficient, even at partial load and they have very low noise level.</p>\n\n<p>Efficiency of these motors is maximized by effective utilization of materials, minimizing losses and optimal design of the fins. Due to the reduced fan and core losses, there is no sharp drop in the efficiency curve at partial loads.</p>\n\n<p>All fan cooled motors feature advanced cooling systems and superior insulation for excellent thermal stability. These motors are ideal for continuous industrial applications requiring energy efficiency and quiet operation.</p>','HV-Fan-Cooled-Motors.webp',1),(21,20,'Energy Efficient Motors HV - N Series','energy-efficient-motors-hv-n-series','Premium Efficiency High Voltage','<p>Energy Efficient Motors HV - N Series from CG are trademarked series of industrial motors offered in air cooled and water cooled construction. These motors are designed keeping in mind the stringent noise, vibration regulations and efficiency requirements of the customer.</p>\n\n<p>Components are designed using finite elements of analysis, structural, thermal and air flow. This ensures better stress distribution and high structural rigidity to achieve higher power to weight ratio.