f=\"tel:+919820042210\">+919820042210</a></li>\n </ul>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"col-xl-2 col-lg-6 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-delay=\"400ms\">\n <div class=\"footer-widget__column footer-widget__social-box\">\n <div class=\"site-footer__social\">\n <a href=\"#\"><i class=\"fab fa-twitter\"></i></a>\n <a href=\"#\"><i class=\"fab fa-facebook\"></i></a>\n <a href=\"#\"><i class=\"fab fa-pinterest-p\"></i></a>\n <a href=\"#\"><i class=\"fab fa-instagram\"></i></a>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"site-footer__bottom\">\n <div class=\"row\">\n <div class=\"col-xl-12\">\n <div class=\"site-footer__bottom-inner\">\n <p class=\"site-footer__bottom-text\">┬⌐ 2023 Bombay Engineering Syndicate. All Rights Reserved.</p>\n <!-- <ul class=\"list-unstyled site-footer__bottom-menu\">\n <li><a href=\"#\">Help</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a></li>\n -->\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>\n </div>',NULL,NULL,0,0),(2,'en',NULL,'about-us','About us',NULL,'<div class=\"container\">\n <h3>Our Presence and Capabilities</h3>\n <p>BES operates from Mumbai (Maharashtra) and Ahmedabad (Gujarat), serving a diverse client base that includes industries, OEMs, EPC contractors, project consultants, infrastructure companies, and retail customers.</p>\n <br />\n <p>We are equipped to handle large-scale project enquiries, complex engineering specifications, and day-to-day retail requirements with equal precision.</p>\n <br />\n <p>Our team is experienced in working with major consultants and EPC firms such as:</p>\n <ul>\n <li>EIL</li>\n <li>TOYO</li>\n <li>L&amp;T</li>\n <li>Lurgi</li>\n <li>Mecons</li>\n <li>Foster Wheeler</li>\n <li>Jacobs</li>\n <li>BHEL</li>\n <li>NTPC</li>\n <li>NPC</li>\n <li>and more</li>\n </ul>\n <br />\n <p>We provide complete documentation support, including pre-tendering guidance, spec-matching, technical datasheets, GA drawings, QAP, inspection coordination, and post-order execution.</p>\n <br /><br />\n <h3>Our Product Range</h3>\n <p>BES offers one of the widest ranges of LV &amp; HV Industrial Motors in India:</p>\n <br />\n <p><strong><span style=\"color:#3498db;\">Types of Motors</span></strong></p>\n <ul>\n <li>LT / HT Industrial Motors</li>\n <li>IE2 / IE3 / IE4 High-Efficiency Motors</li>\n <li>Hazardous Area Motors</li>\n <li>Increased Safety Ex ΓÇ£eΓÇ¥</li>\n <li>Non-Sparking Ex ΓÇ£nΓÇ¥</li>\n <li>Flame Proof Ex ΓÇ£dΓÇ¥ (Gas Group IIA / IIB / IIC)</li>\n <li>Crane Duty Motors</li>\n <li>Ginning Motors</li>\n <li>Textile Motors</li>\n <li>Brake Motors</li>\n <li>Roller Table Motors</li>\n <li>Cooling Tower Motors</li>\n <li>Energy Efficient Motors</li>\n <li>Pressure Booster Pump Motors</li>\n <li>Special Application Motors for OEMs</li>\n </ul>\n <br />\n <p><strong><span style=\"color:#3498db;\">Drives, Controls &amp; Energy-Saving Solutions</span></strong></p>\n <ul>\n <li>AC Variable Frequency Drives (VFDs)</li>\n <li>Soft Starters</li>\n <li>Motor Protection Devices &amp; Starters</li>\n <li>IE3/IE4 energy-efficient upgrades</li>\n <li>Customized power-saving solutions for HVAC, water supply, and industrial processes</li>\n </ul>\n <br /><br />\n <h3>Substitutes for Imported Motors</h3>\n <p>We specialize in providing reliable replacements for imported NEMA and IEC frame motors, offering:</p>\n <ul>\n <li>Faster delivery</li>\n <li>Lower cost of ownership</li>\n <li>Local service support</li>\n <li>High-efficiency equivalents to global brands</li>\n </ul>\n <br />\n <p>Our technical expertise ensures accurate frame matching, RPM matching, shaft dimensions, mounting compatibility, and performance equivalence.</p>\n <br /><br />\n <h3>Industries We Serve</h3>\n <p>Our products cater to a wide spectrum of industries:</p>\n <ul>\n <li>Oil &amp; Gas</li>\n <li>Petrochemicals &amp; Chemicals</li>\n <li>Pharmaceuticals</li>\n <li>Textiles</li>\n <li>Steel &amp; Metal Processing</li>\n <li>Infrastructure &amp; Construction</li>\n <li>Water Supply &amp; Sewage</li>\n <li>HVAC &amp; Building Utilities</li>\n <li>Machine Manufacturers (OEMs)</li>\n <li>Agriculture &amp; Irrigation</li>\n <li>Paper &amp; Pulp</li>\n </ul>\n <br />\n <p>BES is trusted by both large enterprises and small businesses for providing reliable, high-quality motors with assured performance.</p>\n <br /><br />\n <h3>Why Clients Trust BES</h3>\n <ul>\n <li>Γ£ö 65+ years of industry experience</li>\n <li>Γ£ö Only genuine and certified CG / Crompton products</li>\n <li>Γ£ö Technical support for sizing, selection, and troubleshooting</li>\n <li>Γ£ö Prompt service, fast response times, and transparent communication</li>\n <li>Γ£ö Extensive ready stock for fast delivery</li>\n <li>Γ£ö Custom-engineered solutions for critical applications</li>\n <li>Γ£ö End-to-end project support (tendering to commissioning)</li>\n </ul>\n <br />\n <p>Our goal is to provide the most suitable and cost-effective solution for every customer requirementΓÇöensuring long-term reliability, energy savings, and complete customer satisfaction.</p>\n</div>','<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n<div class=\"about-one__right wow fadeInRight\" data-wow-delay=\"500ms\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\n<div class=\"section-title text-left\"><span class=\"section-title__tagline\">about us</span>\n<h2 class=\"section-title__title\">Company Profile</h2>\n</div>\n<p data-end=\"268\" data-start=\"103\"><strong data-end=\"221\" data-start=\"103\">Authorized Channel Partners of CG Power & Industrial Solutions Ltd. and Crompton Greaves Consumer Electricals Ltd.</strong><br data-end=\"224\" data-start=\"221\" />\n<strong data-end=\"268\" data-start=\"224\">Since 1957 ΓÇö The Rotating Machine People</strong></p>\n<p data-end=\"597\" data-start=\"270\">Bombay Engineering Syndicate (BES) is one of IndiaΓÇÖs oldest and most trusted suppliers of <strong data-end=\"437\" data-start=\"360\">Electric Motors, Industrial Drives, and Energy-Efficient Motion Solutions</strong>. Established in 1957, we have over <strong data-end=\"498\" data-